4.2-§. To`rtburchak yasashga doir masalalar

1-masala. a, A, B, (a˄e), (a˄f)  elementlarga ko`ra to`rtburchak   yasang.

Analiz: Izlanayotgan to`rtburchak yasalgan deb faraz qilamiz va uni tahminan chizib olamiz.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 


Berilgan: a, A, B, (a˄e), (a˄f) .

 

 


                                                                                                                  

Reja:                                                                                       

1⁰.Al  nuqtadan a kesmani qo`yamiz, natijada B nuqta hosil bo`ladi.

2⁰. A nuqtadan A ni va  B nuqtadan B ni qo`yamiz. A=BAD, B=ABC.

3⁰. A nuqtadan (a˄e) ni qo`yamiz va bu yerda (a˄e)= BAC.

4⁰. B nuqtadan (a˄f) ni qo`yamiz va bu yerda (a˄f)= ABD.

5⁰. Hosil bo`lgan D va C nuqtalarni tutashtiramiz, natijada biz izlayotgan ABCD to`rburchak hosil bo`ladi.

     Isbotlash:  Yasashga ko`ra.

Tekshirish: A, B,(a˄e), (a˄f)=0⁰,180⁰ da, A+(a˄f)≥180⁰ da,  B+(a˄e) ≥180⁰ da, (a˄f)+(a˄e) ≥180⁰ da yechimga ega emas. Qolgan barcha hollarda yechimga ega.

2-masala. Ma`lum aylanaga bir tomoni va undagi ikki burchagi bo`yicha ichki chizilgan to`rtburchak yasang.

Berilgan: AB= a, A, B.

 

 

 


Analiz: Izlanayotgan to`rtburchak yasalgan deb faraz qilamiz va uni taxminan chizib olamiz.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

        Reja:    1⁰.A nuqtadan  aylana chizamiz, natijada  hosil bo`ladi.

2⁰. A nuqtadan A ni va B nuqtadan B ni qo`yamiz.

3⁰.

4⁰. Hosil bo`lgan D va C nuqtalarni tutashtiramiz, natijada biz izlayotgan ABCD    to`rtburchak                                  

hosil bo`ladi.                                                                                                   

                   Yasash:

 

   

 

       Isbotlash:  Yasashga ko`ra BAD=A, ABC=B, AB=a.

Tekshirish: A, B=0⁰,180⁰ da yechimga ega emas. Qolgan barcha hollarda yechimga ega.

3-masala. Uchta tomoni va bir diagonali bo`yicha shunday to`rtburchak yasangki, unga ichki aylana chizish mumkin bo`lsin.

Berilgan: a,b,c va d-diagonal.

 

 

 


Analiz: Izlanayotgan to`rtburchak yasalgan deb faraz qilamiz va uni tahminan chizib olamiz.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 


Reja:

1⁰. Al – nuqtadan a kesmani qo`yamiz natijada B nuqta hosil bo`ladi.

2⁰. B nuqtadan  (Bu yerda m=a+c-b )

3⁰. A nuqtadan  aylana chizamiz va .

4⁰. C nuqtadan  aylana chizamiz.

5⁰. A nuqtadan aylana chizamiz.

6⁰.

7⁰. Hosil bo`lgan A,B,C  nuqtalarni ketma-ket tutashtiramiz.

Yasash:

                                              

 

 

 

 

Isbotlash:  Yasashga ko`ra AB=a, AD=b, DC=c, AC=d, m=a+b-c. Bundan a+c=b+m ekamlogi kelib chiqadi va bu ABCD to`rtburchakka ichki aylana chizish mumkin.

Tekshirish:  Masala har doim yechimga ega.

Qavariq to`rtburchaklarni yasash uchun kamida uning beshta elementi ma`lum bo`lishi va ulardan kamida ikkitasi chiziqli element bo`lishi shart. To`rtburchak elementlarini quyidagicha (38-rasm) belgilaymiz: |AB|=a, |BC|=b, |CD|=c va |DA|=d, uning diagonallarini |AC|=e, |BD|=f, burchaklarini A, B, C, D, diagonallari orasidagi burchakni - (e˄f). Analiz chizmasida yordamchi figurani shtrixlab ko`rsatamiz.

                 

                                                                                              

 

 

 

          38-rasm                                                                 39-rasm

4.2.1. Quyidagi elementlardan foydalanib, to`rtburchak yasang.

1) a, b, c, d va eb     (39-rasm)

2) a, b, c, d va bir burchagi   (40-rasm)               3) a, b, A, B, C     (41-rasm)

               

 

 

 

4) a, b, c, B, C  (42-rasm)

5) a, A, B, (a˄e), (a˄f)  (43-rasm)

             

                                                                                          

 

 

 

           42-rasm                                                                    43-rasm

6) c, d, A, B, C (44-rasm)

7) a, d, e, (a˄e), (a˄f) (45-rasm)

               

                                                                                                    

 

 

 

            44-rasm                                                              45-rasm

8) a, b, c, e va f (tomonlardan istalgan uchtasini olish mumkin)

9) a, b, c (yoki d), f va  B

10) a, b, f va A, B (46-rasm)

 

 

 

 


                                                                          

                                                              

46-rasm

13) a, b, c, e, C

14) a, b, c, e, D

15) a, b, e, f, (e˄f)

17) a, b, c, e, A

18) a, b, c, B, D

19) a, b, f, B, (e˄f)

20) a, c, e, B, (e˄f)

21)  a, b, A, B, (e˄f)
